            <a href="/blog" class="flex w-full justify-center cursor-pointer items-center gap-2 self-stretch rounded-[4px] border border-[#261819] text-black text-[14px] font-bold font-lato transition-colors hover:bg-black hover:text-white group" style="padding:14px 16px;">
